# RA Coding Test

**Author:** Yuxin Shen

This repository contains my submission for the RA coding test. It includes two tasks:

- **Task 1:** Construct a U.S. county–year panel dataset using BEA and BLS data
- **Task 2:** Download, clean, harmonize, and construct IRS SOI county–year and ZIP–year panel datasets

---

## Repository Structure

```text
RA_Coding_Test/
├── raw_data/
│   ├── bea/
│   ├── bls/
│   └── soi/
│       ├── county/
│       └── zip/
├── code/
│   ├── Task_1_Yuxin_S.Rmd
│   └── Task_2_Yuxin_S.Rmd
├── output/
│   ├── task1_bea_county_panel.csv
│   ├── task1_bls_county_panel.csv
│   ├── task1_county_year_panel.csv
│   ├── task2_soi_county_year_panel.csv
│   └── task2_soi_zip_year_panel.csv
├── docs/
│   ├── task1_data_summary.md
│   └── task2_data_summary.md
└── README.md
